<p>The purpose of <code v-pre>prefix</code> is to abbreviate the links in the same level <code v-pre>items</code> by extracting the common prefix to <code v-pre>prefix</code>, allowing the theme to complete the full link concatenation for you.</p>
<p>It should be noted that only relative path links in <code v-pre>items</code> will be concatenated with <code v-pre>prefix</code>, while absolute paths will not be processed.</p>
